data.description: Now is the time to make the move to Lake Sharon Estates in Corinth, and this Frontier Quick Move-In home is the perfect place to call home. Tall ceilings in the foyer and family room set the stage for this brilliant open-concept layout. Plenty of windows throughout the home illuminate all 3,404 square feet this layout has to offer. With 5 bedrooms, 3.5 bathrooms, and a 2-car garage, there is so much to love about this quality-built home. First impressions are everything, and you'll surely be impressed by this craftsman-style mahogany front door that gives way to warm gray tile wood-look flooring the moment you step foot inside. Add a large desk, a few bookshelves, and a stylish floor lamp to personalize your home office, tucked just off the foyer. Continue past a convenient powder bath and enter the heart of the home. The large island is an entertainer's dream and the 2 pendant lights overhead further elevate the space. Whether you're cooking for a crowd or whipping up a simple weeknight dinner on the go, the top-of-the-line GE® stainless steel appliances will allow you to prepare meals with ease. White-painted cabinetry with undermount lighting illuminates the decorative mosaic tile backsplash and light quartz countertops that wrap the perimeter of the space. You can't forget about the boxed out window in the dining room, offering a little extra seating space and a whole lot of sunlight. A corner fireplace in the family room crea...
